{"tid":2293133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"摩爾多瓦總統大選 莫斯科支持對象承認敗選","createTime":"2020-11-20T04:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T07:06:23.000Z","uid":177168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a6008900e43231cade32100a931a2edfe115c0ce","tid":2293133,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/16/anntw/9085247.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F16%2Fanntw%2F9085247.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=01e02ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯莫斯科當局支持的摩爾多瓦現任總統多東（IgorDodon），今天承認在昨天總統大選第2輪投票中，敗給親歐洲聯盟的挑戰者桑杜（Maia Sandu）。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，多東告訴記者：「初步結果顯示桑杜已經獲勝。」<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，克里姆林宮發言人培斯科夫（DmitryPeskov）今天說，俄國希望與桑杜建立工作關係。<br />\n<br />\n摩爾多瓦是前蘇聯共和國，有350萬人口。48歲的桑杜傾向讓國家與歐洲聯盟（EU）關係更為緊密。<br />\n<br />\n中央選舉委員會公布的初步結果顯示，在完成100%計票後，桑杜得票率57.75%，多東42.25%。<br />\n<br />\n摩爾多瓦選舉備受俄羅斯關注，因為在多個與克里姆林宮同盟的政府飽受政治動盪之際，俄國希望兩極對立的摩爾多瓦能繼續在其影響力之下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5019699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F5019699&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=43f9e279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5019699</a>"},{"pid":"fcde8bd98c36468527a53681e835cc4846029267","tid":2293133,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:45:04.000Z","msg":"竟然變天了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a3c90133ddf16456fd830a7e23ba7af5077a6f","tid":2293133,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"前蘇聯選舉都公正透明過美國紅州"},{"pid":"